          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-5",
        "text": "فَادْخُلِي فِي عِبَادِي وَادْخُلِي جَنَّتِي",
        "font": {
          "family": "Chopin Script",
          "size_px": 24
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 27,
          "y_px": 165.537
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-8",
        "text": "\"My hand is lonely for your clasping, dear; my ear is tired waiting for your call.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Adorable",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -12,
          "y_px": 294.449
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-9",
        "text": "I want your strength to help, your laugh to cheer; Heart, soul and senses need you, one and all.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Adorable",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 3,
          "y_px": 329.864
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-10",
        "text": "I droop without your full, frank sympathy; We ought to be together - you and I.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Adorable",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 3,
          "y_px": 367.302
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-11",
        "text": "We want each other so, to comprehend; The dream, the hope, things planned, or seen, or wrought.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Adorable",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 6,
          "y_px": 405.753
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-12",
        "text": "Companion, comforter and guide and friend; As much as love asks love, does thought ask thought.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Adorable",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 3,
          "y_px": 441.167
        },
        "rotation": {
